<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>فِي مَشْيه تبختر<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span><span class="c2">(تبهنس)</span> فِي مَشْيه بهنس<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span><span class="c2">(البهنس)</span> الْأسد <span class="c2">(ج)</span> بهانس<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>